-- France to Approve Tax Rise in Budget Revision: Echos
-- B y   J a m e s   K r a u s
-- 2012-07-30T20:00:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-30/france-to-approve-tax-rise-in-budget-revision-echos-correct-.html
(Corrects to tomorrow in first paragraph.)  France’s parliament will tomorrow
give its final approval to 7.2 billion euros ($8.8 billion) in
tax increases as part of a revised national budget,  Les Echos 
reported.  The revised budget is due to be validated by the country’s
Constitutional Council next week, the newspaper said.  Editor: To contact the reporter on this story:
